public class ProviderType
extends AbstractPluginSpecification

A Provider type defines what parameters admins and users need to provide to a Provider in order for it to provide machines properly.

Method Detail

groupFields

public PluginFields groupFields(Map<String,String> input)
Given a map of field name to value, filter out all fields that are not admin overridable fields or user fields, and group fields by type. For example, sensitive fields will be grouped together, as will non sensitive fields.

Parameters:
input - Mapping of field name to value.
Returns:
PluginFields containing fields grouped by type.
